lyrics:
[Verse]
Late at night, I'm lost and alone
Searching for someone I can call my own
But every heart I touch, it just turns to stone
No one comes close, no one's ever quite known

[Chorus]
No one comes close, to the love I crave
In this empty silence, my heart's enslaved
No one comes close, to the warmth I yearn
In these cold nights, my soul's destined to burn
